     <div class="bookname"> 
      <h1>正文 第三百一十九章紧急行动</h1> 
      <div class="bottem1"> 
       <a href="87243.html">上一章</a> ← 
       <a href="/files/article/html/5/5380/">章节列表</a> → 
       <a href="87248.html">下一章</a> 
       <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(87244,5380);">加入书签</a> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lm">
       推荐阅读：
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5379/" title="超级优化" target="_blank">超级优化</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5378/" title="驻马太行侧" target="_blank">驻马太行侧</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5377/" title="大周皇族" target="_blank">大周皇族</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5376/" title="超级医警" target="_blank">超级医警</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5372/" title="重生之霸道人生" target="_blank">重生之霸道人生</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5381/" title="制霸空权" target="_blank">制霸空权</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5382/" title="战天" target="_blank">战天</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/5/5383/" title="异世为僧" target="_blank">异世为僧</a>
